                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Just as the Eremites have many offshoots, the various Fatui operating beyond their borders also feature some units with more independent characteristics. One such group faced Aybak and his comrades in a battle, and he thought it to be the hardest fight he had ever experienced. In the end, no one walked away with what they had wanted...",
